// MobileTerminalTabBar
// Horizontally scrollable terminal tab bar optimized for mobile.
// Simplified version of TerminalTabBar: no drag-and-drop, compact sizing.
// Each tab shows the session name (truncated to 80px) and a close (X) button.
// A "+" button at the right adds a new terminal.

FUNCTION MobileTerminalTabBar(tabs, activeTabId, onTabSelect, onTabClose, onTabAdd) -> JSX  EXPORT
  Renders a scrollable row of tab buttons.
  Active tab gets a white/blue highlight; inactive tabs are gray.
  Close button stops click propagation before calling onTabClose.
  Add button calls onTabAdd.
